---
/**
 * Terms & Conditions
 * Terms of use for Woorkeasy.
 */
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Woorkeasy"
  description="Terms and conditions for using Woorkeasy free online tools. All tools provided as-is, no warranties, client-side processing only."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-xl text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p class="body-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-4">Last updated: June 2025</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="space-y-8 body-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using Woorkeasy, you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Use of Service</h2>
        <p>Woorkeasy provides free online tools for personal and commercial use. All tools are provided "as is" without any warranty. You agree to use these tools at your own risk. You are responsible for ensuring that your use of the tools complies with applicable laws and regulations.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Client-Side Processing</h2>
        <p>All tools process data entirely in your browser using JavaScript. No files or data are uploaded to our servers. Since processing happens locally, we cannot guarantee performance across all devices and browsers. Results may vary based on your system capabilities.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>The Woorkeasy name, logo, and website design are our intellectual property. The tools and their underlying code are provided for your use but not for redistribution or commercial resale. You may not copy, modify, or reproduce our tools for commercial purposes without permission.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Woorkeasy shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the website or tools. We make no guarantees regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of the tools or their output.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">External Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites or services (such as Google AdSense). We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of these third-party sites.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:woorkeasy@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">woorkeasy@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
